### User entity HTTP tests
### User 엔티티 관련 API: 회원가입, 로그인, 관리자 회원 조회

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminEmail = hanaro
@adminPassword = 12345678
@signupEmail = entity-user-20260317@test.com
@signupPassword = 12345678
@signupNickname = entityUser0317
@signupPhone = 01055551234

### User 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{signupEmail}}",
  "password": "{{signupPassword}}",
  "nickname": "{{signupNickname}}",
  "phoneNumber": "{{signupPhone}}"
}

### Admin 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### User 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### User 검색 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users?keyword=%ED%98%B8%EB%A1%9D%EC%9D%B4
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### User별 가입 내역 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/2/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### User 비정상 테스트: 중복 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@test.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "nickname": "중복닉네임",
  "phoneNumber": "01077778888"
}

